### Update profile - Success case
PUT {{host}}/api/profiles/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nickname": "업데이트된닉네임",
  "introSentences": [
    "수정된 첫 번째 소개 문장입니다",
    "업데이트된 두 번째 소개입니다",
    "새로운 세 번째 소개 문장"
  ]
}

### Update profile - Only nickname
PUT {{host}}/api/profiles/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nickname": "새닉네임만변경",
  "introSentences": []
}

### Update profile - Validation error (nickname too long)
PUT {{host}}/api/profiles/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nickname": "이닉네임은15자를넘어서에러가발생합니다",
  "introSentences": [
    "정상적인 소개 문장"
  ]
}

### Update profile - Validation error (too many intro sentences)
PUT {{host}}/api/profiles/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nickname": "정상닉네임",
  "introSentences": [
